    "Title": "Jorrit Dossier: Updated Seismic Data",
    "Description": "Hockrow Agency \nCase File #JD10285\nLead Investigator: Arken Mallor\n\nCase Update: \nOne of the biggest issue when it comes to ongoing investigations is intel growing stale. To help alleviate that, I\u2019m going to have you head back into Onyx and grab the latest seismic sensor data. Would be good to see what the latest readings say.\n\nContract Investigator Actions:\nExplore the <EM4>Research</EM4> wing and <EM4>retrieve the Seismic data</EM4> and deliver it to <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>.\n\nAdditional Notes:\nBe wary of possible hostile forces on site.\n \nTravel to Onyx in a vehicle that can be stored in a large hangar.\n\nOnce you hand off this data, I'll send you a <EM4>ASD Secure Drive</EM4> that you can collect at your home location.",
